    "details": {
      "isComplex": true,
      "level": {
        "value": 10
      },
      "disable": "<p>@Check[type:thievery|dc:31] (expert) to jam enough needle holes to prevent the wave from continuing or @Check[type:perception|dc:29] to notice the bypass switch at the entrance of the room.</p>",
      "description": "<p>Thousands of 6-inch-long needles stab out of the walls, floor, and ceiling of this room in waves, creating a beautiful rippling effect.</p><hr /><h3>Conversion notes (this module)</h3><p>Walls, floor, and ceiling stab in rippling waves of six-inch numbing needles a round after entry; the room is difficult terrain while active.</p>",
      "reset": "<p>The trap deactivates and resets when there are no creatures standing in this room or when the bypass switch has been flipped.</p>",
      "routine": "<p>On the trap's turn each round, the wave continues around the room and the trap makes a numbing needle Strike against any creature standing in this room or climbing its walls.</p>"
    },
